title: The Tomb of King Ceremor
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

[[King Ceremor]] was buried  near [[Calden]] and [[Vernwyn]]. No one knows the exact location of his tomb, but it is rumoured that his servants laid him to rest alongside some of the greatest royal treasures. This rumour has caused many adventurers to brave [[The Great Marsh]], but to no avail. 